- `card_back.png` - Card back design for face-down cards

### Fallback

If images are not downloaded, the app automatically uses SVG graphics as fallback. The game works either way!

### Image Optimization

After downloading, you can optimize images:
```bash
# Install imagemin (optional)
npm install -g imagemin-cli imagemin-pngquant

# Optimize all PNG files
imagemin *.png --plugin=pngquant --out-dir=.
```

